stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_compute_digest: fork_digest = compute_fork_digest(genesis_validators_root, epoch)
    q_compute_digest --> q_check_next_fork: check if next fork is planned
    q_check_next_fork --> q_no_fork: no future fork planned
    q_check_next_fork --> q_has_fork: future fork planned
    q_no_fork --> q_set_no_fork: next_fork_version = current_fork_version, next_fork_epoch = FAR_FUTURE_EPOCH
    q_has_fork --> q_check_bpo: check if next fork is regular or BPO
    q_check_bpo --> q_regular_fork: regular fork (version changes)
    q_check_bpo --> q_bpo_fork: BPO fork (version unchanged)
    q_regular_fork --> q_set_regular: next_fork_version = planned fork version, next_fork_epoch = planned epoch
    q_bpo_fork --> q_set_bpo: next_fork_version = current_fork_version, next_fork_epoch = planned epoch
    q_set_no_fork --> q_encode: encode ENRForkID(fork_digest, next_fork_version, next_fork_epoch)
    q_set_regular --> q_encode: encode ENRForkID(fork_digest, next_fork_version, next_fork_epoch)
    q_set_bpo --> q_encode: encode ENRForkID(fork_digest, next_fork_version, next_fork_epoch)
    q_encode --> [*]: return SSZ-encoded eth2 field
